</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院全体教师<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教师申报课题，分院审核通过后分院领导签字盖章报科研处、教务处等部门，由科研处、教务处作最后的审核、审批等工作。项目建立后公示项目</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">名称、主持人和参加人员、级别、经费及经费使用情况、计划完成时间等。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">校园网公示三天<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教师教学任务安排</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"68\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">每学期期末或期初</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院全体教师</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">根据教务处下达教学任务，由各教研室主任负责具体落实项任务</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">公告栏、<span>FTP</span>上公示一周</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教师教学工作量统计<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"68\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">每学期期末</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院全体教师</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">下发工作量统计表，每位教师填完后交教研室审核，后交分院审核统计</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">公告栏、<span>FTP</span>公告</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">公示一周</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教学检查情况</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"68\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">每学期期初、期中、期末</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分 院</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">全体教师<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">配合学院教务处安排，在期初、期中、期末进行教学检查，个教研室上交各类检查表，督导反馈检查及听课情况，有问题及时反馈</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院教师会议上通报教学检查情况，特殊情况个别通知或谈话</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教改教研项目申报</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"68\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">以学期中教务处通知为准</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院全体教师</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">根据教师个人意愿上报教改教研项目，分院进行审核汇总后上报教务处</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">公告栏、<span>FTP</span>公告</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">公示一周</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教师教学业绩考核</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"68\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">每学年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院全体教师</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">依据学院教师业绩考核办法制订分院考核细则；<span>2</span>公布分院教师业绩考核细则；<span>3.</span>对分院全体任课教师进行教师业绩考核（按照学院业绩考核办法从<span>M1</span>、<span>M2</span>、<span>M3 </span>三个方面进行考核，确定每位教师考核等级）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">公告栏、<span>FTP</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">公示一周</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">教学、科研实验设备的购置<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"68\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">每学年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院全体教师</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">相关教研室、部门提出书面申请，分院党政领导班子审核通过后设备购置单，（如果需要购置大宗设备，则需先打申请报告给设备处，由设备处组织专家论证是否有购买的必要。）填妥后由设备处负责人签字盖章。接着到课题归属部门签字盖章签字，再由学院主管领导审查签字后交给设备处，<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">校园网上发公告、公示一般不少于<span>7</span>天<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">语音实验室安排<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"68\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">每学期<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"96\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院全体教师</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"244\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">由英语教研室主任根据每个班的人数、以往语音室的排课情况， 公平公正的来分配语音室。排课完毕后，一般会将课表放供教师参考， 如有问题或建议， 可反馈给实验室主任进行微调，<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"117\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">分院<span>FTP </span>上公示一周<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:black;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:black;\">三、</span><span style=\"color:black;\">公开工作形式多样，渠道畅通，反馈及时<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、教职工代表大会制度<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">教代会是学校民主管理和民主监督的基本组织形式和制度，是校务公开的基本载体。学校建立健全教代制度，并根据不同的内容，分别由教代会审议通过或审议决定。增强了工作透明度，加强了教职工对学院工作的全面了解，使教职工民主参与、民主管理、民主监督的作用得以更好的发挥。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、提案征集、落实与反馈制度<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">学校坚持在教代会召开之前征集提案，并及时认真做好提案的答复、落实、公开、反馈与跟踪工作，提案回复率达<span>100</span>％。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、院信息公开栏的公示制度<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">设立院务公开栏，凡涉及师生员工切身利益的重要事项，教职工关心的热点、难点问题，都在校院（处）务公开栏上予以公示，并<span>实施了各种事务公开“双轨制”（即以传统的文件印发形式和电子公告形式）</span>公开。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、会议通报制度<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">学院把召开各种会议作为院务公开的重要形式，畅通学院与教职工的联系。如：院长在新学期全院教职工大会上作工作部署报告；在各阶段工作会议上通报学校的重大事项；根据教职工关心的热点、难点问题，不定期召开各类行政人员会议、党员会议、教师代表座谈会、分院督导会议等，通报学校和行政部门的工作情况。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、人文学院</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">内网或<span>ftp</span>（文本存档）</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">公开制度<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">充分利用人文<span>学院</span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">内网或<span>ftp</span>（文本存档），</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">拓宽院务公开的渠道，及时上传院务公开材料，使广大教职工及时了解学校改革、发展、建设的重大事项和与教职工切身利益密切相关的方案和决策。并做好校公开网的维护和信息更新工作。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">、其他院务公开渠道<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">学院的重要工作部署、上级的决定、工作要点和总结等，都通过相关公开途径传达到各教研室，并利用学院宣传栏、人文<span>QQ</span>群等宣传媒体进行公开；同时，在人文学院通讯录上公开院长、书记的个人通讯地址、<span>QQ</span>号和电子信箱。对有普遍性的问题，领导和有关部门都予以公开答复，对比较重大、涉及面广的问题，经研究后予以回复。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">四、<span>院务公开工作取得的成效<span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">通过院务公开，使学院的管理过程公开化、规范化，大大促进了学院决策的民主化、科学化和法制化，进一步提高了学院整体管理水平，有效地促进了干部作风建设，保证了教职工的知情权、参与权和监督权，使教职工的民主权利、切身利益得到了保障，消除了不必要的误会和矛盾，使教职工群众关心的难点问题得到化解，从而有效地激发了广大教职工参政议政的主人翁责任感，增强了凝聚力，为学院改革与发展创造更为良好的内部环境。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\">五、今后努力方向<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:black;\">2010</span><span style=\"color:black;\">——<span>2011</span>年度院务公开工作在学院党政班子的正确领导和广大教职工的配合下，取得了一定的成效，但是仍存在公开程序不够规范，以及随意性、盲目性等问题。在今后的工作中，我们将进一步加强领导，完善工作机制，加大对院务公开工作的协调、检查和监督，学习、宣传有关院务公开工作的文件，认真落实院务公开责任制，增强院务公开工作的规范性，扎实推进院务公开工作，进一步保障广大教职工的知情权、参与权和监督权，为促进我院的改革、发展，为构建和谐、平安校园做出新的贡献。<span> </span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>', '', '', 'admin', '管理员', '', '12', '19', '人文信息公开', '3', '2012-05-06 13:36:15', '', '', '2', '', null, '人文学院院务公开工作报告（定稿）', '1', null, '1');
INSERT INTO `ws_information` VALUES ('25', null, '&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:90pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:14pt;\">《应用文写作》课程标准（专用）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:24pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">课程代码：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">课程性质：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">培训课程</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">学时学分：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">——</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">学时，</span><span>1.5</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">学分</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">一、课程设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（一）课程性质</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">《应用文写作》是重要的交际工具，是人类文化的重要组成部分。工具性与人文性的统一，是《应用文写作》课程的基本特点。《应用文写作》是我院公共必修课之一，它对学生职业能力的培养和职业素养的养成具有不可或缺的支撑作用，同时，它也是学生全面发展和终身发展的重要基础。本课程教学的主要目的是通过理论与实践教学，提高学生的写作水平、交际能力、审美素质和文化品位，塑造学生的人文精神，使学生真正成为德、智、体、美等全面发展的人。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（二）课程设计</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本课程设计的基本理念是：正确把握应用文写作教育的特点，积极倡导自主、合作、探究的学习方式，努力建设开放而有活力的应用文写作课程，全面提高学生的写作素养和能力，着重训练学生的思维能力、分析能力、社交能力、语言表述能力。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本课程设计的基本思路是：在完成好<span>“</span>应用文写作<span>”</span>课程教学的同时，安排<span>“</span>应用文写作<span>”</span>的延伸教学，将<span>“</span>应用文写作<span>”</span>与其专业课程结合起来，并能针对学生所在岗位的不同需要有的放矢。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">二、课程目标</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（一）知识与技能</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注重语言感受、能力培养二大知识维度的教学，通过本课程的学习，学生应达到下列要求：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:26pt;\">\r\n	<span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、具有较强的阅读理解能力和语言感受能力。了解应用文写作的意义，正确把握材料的内容、文章结构，应用文的文体特点及其写作规范。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:26pt;\">\r\n	<span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、具有较强的写作能力。能根据写作的目的和对象，围绕中心选取材料，合理安排文章结构，同时根据表达的需要，恰当运用适合不同应用文的表达方式。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、具有一定的写作技能与技巧。熟悉商务文书﹑一般应用文的格式，基本掌握常用应用文的写作技能与技巧。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（二）过程与方法</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、在教学理念上，注重从一开始就培养学生自觉的应用文文体意识，让他们认识到写作能力不仅仅是交往工具，而且是同世界有着隐秘关联的文化载体，是自己工作的必需。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、在教材选用和教学内容选取上，将时代性和实践性作为两个重要的元素带入其中，应尽力避免以往那种明显重理论薄实践的思维模式，大胆引进贴近现代、当代生活的范文，尽可能地避免教材滞后于时代的被动状态，以便更好地唤起学生学习应用文写作的积极性和主动性。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、在教学模式上，可以将单篇教学和专题教学结合起来。一个好的专题不仅可以将更多信息带入课堂，而且可能会让许多作品焕发新的意义，进而扩大其可释空间，增益其魅力，同时也能调动学生的学习兴趣，扩大其认知视野和理解空间，并且在整个教学过程中，如果专题与专题之间衔接得好，更会获得事半功倍的效果。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:20pt;\">\r\n	<span>4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、在教学手段上，普及多媒体教学是大势所趋，而适当地引进视频、动漫等当代流行的艺术语言则会与应用文写作教学构成巨大的互动。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:15pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（三）情感态度与价值观</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通过引导学生感受、领悟语言文字的巨大魅力而引领学生为自己工作的需要主动学习应用文写作。引导学生调整好心理素质，正确认识自己的写作能力。激发学生的想象力与创造力，倡导学生的独立精神与合作意识，培育和滋养其健全的人格与社会关怀意识以及社会责任感。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">三、课程内容和标准</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<table style=\"width:428pt;border-collapse:collapse;\" class=\"ke-zeroborder\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"571\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"32%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">教学内容</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">（工作任务、教学单元、模块）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"29%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">知识内容与要求</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"25%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">技能内容与要求</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"12%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">参考学时</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"32%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:31pt;\">\r\n					<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">绪论</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"29%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">掌握常用应用文术语</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"25%\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">懂得在不同语境运用不同应用文术语 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"12%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"32%\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">常用公文模块</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">函</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"29%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">掌握公文函和商务函的用途、写法</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"25%\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">能根据具体的目的拟写</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"12%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"32%\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">通告、通知、通报</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"29%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">了解通知、通告、通报的作用、写法</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"25%\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">能根据具体的目的拟写</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"12%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"32%\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\">事务文书模块<span> &nbsp;</span></span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">计划、总结</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:black 1pt solid;border-left:black 1pt solid;border-top:black 1pt solid;border-right:black 1pt solid;\" width=\"29%\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;\">了解计划、总结的作用、写法</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span