er-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"108\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">常务副所长<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" width=\"206\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">所在党总支（支部）<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" width=\"207\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">人文<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" width=\"98\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">入党时间<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"108\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:6.75pt;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">1993</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">、<span>6</span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"99\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">公开<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">承诺<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">内容<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"520\" colspan=\"7\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:31.8pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">本人作为党员之一份，严格按照学院“八个一”要求，现公开承诺：<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:31.8pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">、认真</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">上好一门课《思想道德修养与法律基础》；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:31.8pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">、高质完成一项课题《农民工子女权利保障研究》；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:31.8pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">、联系一个班级：<span>2010</span>年级工商管理（<span>1</span>）班；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"margin-left:31.8pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">、帮助一个困难学生：<span>2010</span>年级工商管理（<span>1</span>）班学生；<span>5</span>、上好一门公开课：《职业、就业与法律实务》；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:3.8pt;margin-left:28.05pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">、联系一个支部：<span>2010</span>年级工商管理（<span>1</span>）班支部；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"margin-left:31.8pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">、结对一个寝室：<span>2010</span>年级工商管理（<span>1</span>）班学生寝室；<span>8</span>、联系一个积极份子：<span>2010</span>年级工商管理（<span>1</span>）班学生。</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:28pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:203pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">承诺人（签名）：<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:right;\" align=\"right\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#333333;font-size:14pt;\">年<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span>月<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span>日<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" width=\"99\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">党支部<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">审定意见<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"520\" colspan=\"7\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">支部书记（签名）：<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">党组织（盖章）<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:right;\" align=\"right\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">年<span><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span>月<span><span>&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>日<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"99\">\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"4\">\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"103\">\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"1\">\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"103\">\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"103\">\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"98\">\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;\" width=\"108\">\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:14pt;\">注：承诺书一式三份，本人存一份，党支部存一份，公示一份。</span>\r\n</p>', null, '2012-05-29', 'admin', '管理员', null, '0', '20', '党员承诺书', '3', '2012-06-01 22:17:55', null, null, '2', null, null, '党员公开承诺书（韩世强）', '1', null, '1');
