̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">附件下载</span><span><a href=\"http://www.zjff.net/uploads/notice/file/2011_02/28/163012.doc\"><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#575644;font-size:10pt;\">二级学院初审工作说明<span>.doc</span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;\">http://www.zjff.net/notice_show.php?id=35159</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', '', '2012-05-29', 'admin', '管理员', '', '3', '43', '学院通知与报导', '3', '2012-05-29 17:11:14', '', '', '2', '', null, '关于各分院组织2011年专升本报名的通知', '1', null, '1');
INSERT INTO `ws_information` VALUES ('143', '', '<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">2011<span>年专升本《数学》考前培训通知</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';color:#333333;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#666666;font-size:10pt;\">来源：人文学院<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>时间：</span><span>2011-03-02&nbsp;11:29</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';color:#666666;font-size:10pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">各二级学院：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">　　专升本考试在即，为提高学生应考能力和水平，人文学院数理教研室开设专升本数学考前培训，将结合考试大纲要求，结合考情分析、知识点讲解和总结、以及典型例题解析，从掌握知识与运用的角度全面讲解考试所要求的内容，帮助考生运用学科知识，提高解题能力，讲解答题思路，传授应试技巧，为考生应考奠定坚实基础、树立坚定信心。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">　　一、辅导内容：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">　　<span>1.</span><span>按大纲讲授重点内容，典型例题分析，教授解题技巧。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">　　<span>2.</span><span>归纳总结，查漏补缺，考前答疑。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">　　<span>3.</span><span>具体辅导内容安排：周日上课</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"92\">\r\n					<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">次数（日期）&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"202\">\r\n					<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">授课内容涵盖&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"68\">\r\n					<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">教科书必读&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"middle\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"92\">\r\n					<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\">1<span>（</span><span>3</span><span>月</span><span>12</span><span>日）&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\"></span> \r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"202\">\r\n					<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';color:#333333;font-size:10pt;\